### Using EPICS in Your Code

```python
from osprey.utils.epics_utils import EPICSManager

# Create manager (uses configured gateway)
epics_mgr = EPICSManager()

# Read PV values
value = epics_mgr.safe_caget("YOUR:PV:NAME")
```

For more information, see the [EPICS Facility Configuration Guide](https://github.com/als-apg/osprey/blob/main/docs/EPICS_FACILITY_CONFIGURATION.md).

